{"type":"text","timestamp":1773483480399,"sessionID":"ses_314277f9bffeVWfnq7bm5y0Dtk","part":{"id":"prt_cebda2e950010hItuC7dB2Wx4X","sessionID":"ses_314277f9bffeVWfnq7bm5y0Dtk","messageID":"msg_cebda241200196C794q8w7FnTs","type":"text","text":"Now I have a thorough understanding of the code. Let me identify the specific improvements needed:\n\n1. **WishlistPicker tags in list view**: `item.tags.join(\", \")` on line 333 is NOT escaped with `escapeBlessedTags` — if tags contain `{` or `}`, they'll be interpreted as blessed markup.\n2. **WishlistPicker empty list detail pane**: Shows \"No item selected\" — should guide user to CLI command for adding items.\n3. **WishlistOverlay tags**: Same issue on line 603 — tags not escaped.\n4. **WishlistStore addItem**: Should trim text and validate non-empty to prevent blank entries.\n5. **WishlistPicker**: The `selectedIndex` could go out of range on empty list during keyboard navigation (the `promoteToErrand`/`promoteToGenesis`/`deleteSelected` have guards but `refreshDetail` itself shows \"No item selected\" which is fine).\n\nLet me now implement these fixes:","time":{"start":1773483480398,"end":1773483480398}}}
