{"type":"text","timestamp":1773483674492,"sessionID":"ses_314277f9bffeVWfnq7bm5y0Dtk","part":{"id":"prt_cebdccdc1002YxP66g2aGTVnWN","sessionID":"ses_314277f9bffeVWfnq7bm5y0Dtk","messageID":"msg_cebdcc2fc001Dtdzkh1A5QjoVC","type":"text","text":"## Goal\n\nImplement the \"Wishlist/idea jotter in TUI\" feature (`tui-wishlist` branch). The task involves integration and polish for the wishlist feature: wire W key into Quest Picker and Task Browser status bars, verify end-to-end flow (add idea → view list → promote to errand/quest), handle edge cases (empty list, long text wrapping, special characters in YAML), and add a CLI `wishlist` subcommand.\n\n## Instructions\n\n- Use conventional commits: `feat(tui-wishlist):`, `fix(tui-wishlist):`, etc.\n- Commit after each logical unit of work\n- Do NOT squash commits, do NOT push to remote, do NOT modify `tasks`\n- Run `bun run build` to verify everything works before considering done\n- When starting servers, use `portless run <command>`\n\n## Discoveries\n\n- **YAML special chars are already handled correctly** by the `yaml` v2 library — it auto-quotes strings containing `:`, `{`, `}`, `\"`, `#`, `*`, multiline text. Round-trip verified. No changes needed to YAML opts.\n- **W key is already wired** into both Quest Picker (`tui-quest-picker.ts` line 318) and Task Browser (`tui-browser.ts` line 614-617). Status bars already show W keybind hints. The full-screen `WishlistPicker` and modal `WishlistOverlay` both exist and work.\n- **The promote-to-errand and promote-to-genesis flows** are already wired in `tui.ts` (`handleWishlistFlow`, `showWishlistPicker`, `maybeDeleteWishlistItem`).\n- **No CLI `wishlist` subcommand exists** — the detail pane references `woco wishlist add \"your idea\"` but the command doesn't exist yet. This is a critical gap.\n- The branch started at the same commit as `main` (no divergence).\n- Build and typecheck both pass (verified multiple times).\n\n## Accomplished\n\n### Completed:\n1. ✅ Explored codebase thoroughly, identified gaps and edge cases\n2. ✅ Verified YAML special character handling (no changes needed)\n3. ✅ Fixed blessed tag escaping in `WishlistPicker` list view (tags with `{`/`}` were not escaped)\n4. ✅ Fixed blessed tag escaping in `WishlistOverlay` list display (same issue)\n5. ✅ Improved empty wishlist detail pane with actionable getting-started hints\n6. ✅ Hardened `wishlist-store.ts` `addItem()`: trims text, rejects empty, trims/filters tags\n7. ✅ Committed: `fix(tui-wishlist): escape blessed tags in wishlist views and harden store input` (commit `3abdf54`)\n\n### In Progress (PARTIALLY DONE — code edits started but NOT compiled/committed):\n8. 🔄 **Adding CLI `wishlist` subcommand** (`woco wishlist add/list/delete`). The following edits have been made to `src/index.ts` but the `handleWishlistSubcommand` function body has NOT been written yet:\n   - Added `w` and `wl` aliases to `COMMAND_ALIASES`\n   - Added `WISHLIST_SUBCOMMAND_ALIASES` (`a`→add, `ls`→list, `rm`/`del`/`d`→delete)\n   - Added wishlist subcommand parsing in `parseArgs` (similar to quest/tasks)\n   - Added `wishlistTags?: string[]` to `CLIArgs` interface\n   - Added `--tag` flag parsing in the arg switch\n   - Added `case \"wishlist\"` to the main command switch (calls `handleWishlistSubcommand` which doesn't exist yet — **LSP error**)\n   - Added import for `addWishlistItem`, `deleteWishlistItem`, `listWishlistItems` from `wishlist-store.ts`\n   - **STILL NEEDED**: Write the `handleWishlistSubcommand` function body (should go before the error handlers near line ~1146). It needs `add`, `list`, `delete`, and `help` subcommands.\n   - **STILL NEEDED**: Add wishlist to the help text (`cmdHelp` function, around line 478)\n   - **STILL NEEDED**: Run typecheck + build to verify\n\n### Not Started:\n9. ❌ Update help text to include wishlist subcommand documentation\n10. ❌ Final `bun run build` verification\n\n## Relevant files / directories\n\n- **`src/lib/wishlist-store.ts`** — CRUD for wishlist YAML storage (edited: hardened `addItem`)\n- **`src/lib/tui-wishlist.ts`** — `WishlistPicker` (full-screen) and `WishlistOverlay` (modal popup) classes (edited: tag escaping, empty state)\n- **`src/lib/tui-quest-picker.ts`** — Quest Picker with W key binding (read, no changes needed)\n- **`src/lib/tui-browser.ts`** — Task Browser with W key binding and WishlistOverlay toggle (read, no changes needed)\n- **`src/commands/tui.ts`** — Main TUI loop with `handleWishlistFlow`, `showWishlistPicker`, `maybeDeleteWishlistItem` (read, no changes needed)\n- **`src/index.ts`** — CLI entry point (**actively being edited** — wishlist command routing added but `handleWishlistSubcommand` function body is missing, causing LSP error)\n- **`package.json`** — Build config (read only)","time":{"start":1773483674491,"end":1773483674491}}}
