{"type":"text","timestamp":1773483694825,"sessionID":"ses_314277f9bffeVWfnq7bm5y0Dtk","part":{"id":"prt_cebdd8a86002jT7hY40iykIibh","sessionID":"ses_314277f9bffeVWfnq7bm5y0Dtk","messageID":"msg_cebdd8360001o3JD9WOmwTuRce","type":"text","text":"Now I have a clear picture. I need to:\n\n1. Fix the duplicate `--tag` case in the switch statement (there are two `--tag` entries - one under \"General flags\" and one under \"Wishlist-specific options\")\n2. Write the `handleWishlistSubcommand` function\n3. Add wishlist to the help text\n4. Verify typecheck + build","time":{"start":1773483694825,"end":1773483694825}}}
