{"type":"text","timestamp":1773483811408,"sessionID":"ses_314277f9bffeVWfnq7bm5y0Dtk","part":{"id":"prt_cebdf41bc0023D6sM77feZZOd9","sessionID":"ses_314277f9bffeVWfnq7bm5y0Dtk","messageID":"msg_cebdf3b590016r3l0zKJlAk0nw","type":"text","text":"Everything is clean and complete. Here's the summary of what was accomplished across both sessions on this branch:\n\n## Completed Work (2 commits on `feature/tui-wishlist`)\n\n### Commit 1: `3abdf54` — `fix(tui-wishlist): escape blessed tags in wishlist views and harden store input`\n- **Fixed blessed tag escaping** in `WishlistPicker` and `WishlistOverlay` — text containing `{` or `}` characters (common in code ideas) no longer causes rendering errors\n- **Hardened `wishlist-store.ts` `addItem()`** — trims whitespace, rejects empty strings, trims/filters tags\n- **Improved empty wishlist UX** — detail pane shows actionable getting-started hints instead of a blank area\n\n### Commit 2: `af159e1` — `feat(tui-wishlist): add CLI wishlist subcommand (add/list/delete)`\n- **`woco wishlist add \"idea\" [--tag <tag>]`** — capture ideas from CLI with optional categorization tags\n- **`woco wishlist list`** — display all items with short IDs, dates, and tags\n- **`woco wishlist delete <id>`** — remove items by full UUID or short prefix match\n- **Command aliases**: `w` and `wl` → `wishlist`; subcommand aliases: `a`→add, `ls`→list, `rm`/`del`/`d`→delete\n- **Fixed duplicate `--tag` switch case** — disambiguates upgrade tags vs wishlist categorization tags based on command context\n- **Updated help text** with wishlist subcommands, aliases, and examples\n- ✅ Typecheck passes, build passes, working tree clean","time":{"start":1773483811407,"end":1773483811407}}}
